data.title: Station Film
data.meta_description: Station Film | 2,015 followers on LinkedIn. Bicoastal/international production company with a roster of award-winning directors. | Since its launch in 2008, bicoastal/international Station Film quickly established itself as one of the industry’s top creative shops. Its roster of award-winning directors excels at cross-platform storytelling— from film, television, and music videos to VR/AR and digital creation. Station Film’s partners are Stephen Orent, Caroline Gibney, and Michelle Towse.
